SALESFORCE RELEASE NOTES
Einstein for Developers (Beta)

Einstein for Developers is an AI-powered developer tool that’s available as an easy-to-install Visual Studio Code extension built using CodeGen, the secure, custom AI model from Salesforce. Einstein for Developers is enabled in all Salesforce orgs by default.

Read the weekly release notes to learn about recent updates.

Get Started Faster on Einstein for Developers with the New Documentation Site

The new documentation site has a UI that is more consistent with other developer guides. The new site aggregates all the documentation for Einstein for Developers (beta) in a site that’s easier to navigate. Requests to the old documentation site redirect to the new site.
